Bixby to his wife, Debby Bixby, dated June 25, [1933], on stationery from China Airways Federal Inc.; one or more pages missing from original document; includes description of socializing with Max Polin, [William L.] Bond, Mr. Klauk (Pan American Airways auditor), and Mr. Dixon from Standard Oil.
